B | C | C&amp;#9839;/D&amp;#9837; | D | D&amp;#9839;/E&amp;#9837; | E | F | F&amp;#9839;/G&amp;#9837; | G | G&amp;#9839;/A&amp;#9837; | A | A&amp;#9839;/B&amp;#9837; &#13;
